How can drone imagery and open source tools on GitHub help build sustainable communities for refugees?
This is the story of how UNHCR, the UN Refugee Agency ( @UNRefugeeAgency ), worked with partners to transform aerial images into vital maps for refugees in Kakuma and Kalobeyei.
